name: Dashboard for guest user
description: Validate different component for guest user on home page
descriptionHtml: Validate different component for guest user on home page

testStage.description: Validate different component for guest user on home page

steps.name: I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I check that the application text: "Afternoon " isn't empty
I check that the "User Greeting" message is displayed
I check that the "Sign In Sign Up" button is displayed
I get the text from "Store Widget" on Home Screen
I check that the application text: "NEAREST STATION" isn't empty
I check that the "Fuel widget" is displayed
I click on "Sign In Sign Up" button on Home Page
I get the text from the top text area on the "Sign In Screen"
I check that the application text: "Sign In or Sign Up To Get Started." is equals to expected value: "Sign In or Sign Up To Get Started."

parameters.name: Actual:
parameters.value: Sign In or Sign Up To Get Started.

parameters.name: Expected:
parameters.value: Sign In or Sign Up To Get Started.
